<div class="content" name="SYSTEM_SCOPED_POLICY_ID_ACE" uuid="aa0c0f62-4b4c-44f0-9718-c266a6accd9f"><p>The SYSTEM_SCOPED_POLICY_ID_ACE structure defines an ACE for
the purpose of applying a central access policy to the resource.</p><table>
